Class BaseFixtureForAPI

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.pom.crimson.base.BaseFixture
      • com.pom.crimson.base.BaseFixtureForAPI
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    AIAOctaControllerAPITest, CdsControllerAPITest, ContentActionControllerAPITest, ContentControllerAPITest, ContentRootControllerAPITest, GroupAdviceAPITest, MasterDataControllerAPITest, MilestonesControllerAPITest, MomentsControllerAPITest, MomentsRootControllerAPITest, UserProfileControllerAPITest

    public class BaseFixtureForAPI
extends BaseFixture
    BaseFixtureAPI class contains functions which run before starting API test and after test finishes execution. This is an extension of BaseFixture class where the code related to APPIUM, Web driver initialization are removed as they are not applicable for API test. Configuration data like deviceName,platformName,Activity name, Package name etc is fetched from properties and testng.xml
    Author:
    Sivaprakash.Selvaraj
